---
import TestimonialCard from "../../components/TestimonialCard.astro";
import GoogleIcon from "../../icons/GoogleIcon.astro";
import NextArrowIcon from "../../icons/NextArrowIcon.astro";
import PreviousArrow from "../../icons/PreviousArrow.astro";
import StarIcon from "../../icons/StarIcon.astro";
---

<section id="opiniones" class="bg-[#1E1E1E] py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <p
                class="text-[#D4AF37] text-xs! font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3"
            >
                Testimonios
            </p><h2
                class="text-3xl! md:text-4xl! xl:text-5xl! font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6"
            >
                Lo que dicen <span class="text-[#D4AF37]"
                    >nuestros clientes</span
                >
            </h2><a
                href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Pulimentos+Ruiz+Sevilla"
                target="_blank"
                rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-full px-5 py-2.5 hover:scale-105 transition-transform cursor-pointer"
                ><span class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <GoogleIcon />
                </span><div class="flex gap-0.5">
                    <span
                        class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                    >
                        <StarIcon />
                    </span><span
                        class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                        ><StarIcon /></span
                    ><span
                        class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                        ><StarIcon /></span
                    ><span
                        class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                        ><StarIcon /></span
                    ><span
                        class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                        ><StarIcon /></span
                    >
                </div><span class="text-[#333] font-semibold text-sm"
                    >4.9/5 en Google Reviews</span
                ></a
            >
        </div><div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 transition-all duration-700 opacity-100 translate-y-0"
        >
            <div
                class="rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 bg-[#161616]"
            >
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <img
                        alt="María García - cliente de Pulimentos Ruiz Sevilla"
                        class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full object-cover object-top border-2 border-[#D4AF37] shrink-0"
                        loading="lazy"
                        src="https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20woman%20portrait%20smiling%20friendly%20face%20neutral%20background%20Spain%2040%20years%20old&width=80&height=80&seq=avatar-01&orientation=squarish"
                    /><div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-base">
                            María García
                        </p><p class="text-[#B0B0B0] text-xs mb-2">
                            Propietaria de vivienda, Triana
                        </p><div class="flex gap-0.5">
                            <span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div><span
                        class="text-[#D4AF37]/30 font-serif text-5xl leading-none shrink-0 ml-auto"
                        >“</span
                    >
                </div><p
                    class="text-[#C5C5C5] text-sm leading-relaxed mt-4 italic"
                >
                    Increíble resultado. Tenía el suelo de mármol completamente
                    opaco y lleno de rayaduras. Después del pulido y acristalado
                    parece nuevo. El equipo fue muy profesional, puntual y
                    dejaron todo limpio. 100% recomendable.
                </p>
            </div><div
                class="rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent border-2 border-[#D4AF37]/30"
            >
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 flex-row-reverse">
                    <img
                        alt="Carlos Rodríguez - cliente de Pulimentos Ruiz Sevilla"
                        class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full object-cover object-top border-2 border-[#D4AF37] shrink-0"
                        loading="lazy"
                        src="https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20man%20portrait%20smiling%20friendly%20face%20neutral%20background%20Spain%2055%20years%20old&width=80&height=80&seq=avatar-02&orientation=squarish"
                    /><div class="flex-1 text-right">
                        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-base">
                            Carlos Rodríguez
                        </p><p class="text-[#B0B0B0] text-xs mb-2">
                            Presidente comunidad, Los Remedios
                        </p><div class="flex gap-0.5">
                            <span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div><span
                        class="text-[#D4AF37]/30 font-serif text-5xl leading-none shrink-0 mr-auto"
                        >“</span
                    >
                </div><p
                    class="text-[#C5C5C5] text-sm leading-relaxed mt-4 italic"
                >
                    Contratamos a Pulimentos Ruiz para restaurar el terrazo de
                    toda la comunidad. El resultado fue espectacular. Precio
                    justo, trabajo impecable y en el plazo acordado. Los vecinos
                    están encantados.
                </p>
            </div><div
                class="rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 bg-[#161616]"
            >
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <img
                        alt="Ana Martínez - cliente de Pulimentos Ruiz Sevilla"
                        class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full object-cover object-top border-2 border-[#D4AF37] shrink-0"
                        loading="lazy"
                        src="https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20woman%20portrait%20smiling%20confident%20face%20neutral%20background%20Spain%2045%20years%20old&width=80&height=80&seq=avatar-03&orientation=squarish"
                    /><div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-base">
                            Ana Martínez
                        </p><p class="text-[#B0B0B0] text-xs mb-2">
                            Directora de hotel, Centro Sevilla
                        </p><div class="flex gap-0.5">
                            <span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div><span
                        class="text-[#D4AF37]/30 font-serif text-5xl leading-none shrink-0 ml-auto"
                        >“</span
                    >
                </div><p
                    class="text-[#C5C5C5] text-sm leading-relaxed mt-4 italic"
                >
                    Llevamos 3 años trabajando con ellos para el mantenimiento
                    de los suelos del hotel. Siempre disponibles, siempre con el
                    mismo nivel de calidad. Son nuestros proveedores de
                    confianza para el pulido de suelos en Sevilla.
                </p>
            </div><div
                class="rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent border-2 border-[#D4AF37]/30"
            >
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 flex-row-reverse">
                    <img
                        alt="José Luis Fernández - cliente de Pulimentos Ruiz Sevilla"
                        class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full object-cover object-top border-2 border-[#D4AF37] shrink-0"
                        loading="lazy"
                        src="https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20man%20portrait%20smiling%20business%20face%20neutral%20background%20Spain%2050%20years%20old&width=80&height=80&seq=avatar-04&orientation=squarish"
                    /><div class="flex-1 text-right">
                        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-base">
                            José Luis Fernández
                        </p><p class="text-[#B0B0B0] text-xs mb-2">
                            Promotor inmobiliario, Sevilla
                        </p><div class="flex gap-0.5">
                            <span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            ><span
                                class="w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37]"
                                ><i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i></span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div><span
                        class="text-[#D4AF37]/30 font-serif text-5xl leading-none shrink-0 mr-auto"
                        >“</span
                    >
                </div><p
                    class="text-[#C5C5C5] text-sm leading-relaxed mt-4 italic"
                >
                    Los contraté para una rehabilitación completa de suelos de
                    piedra natural en un edificio histórico. Trabajo delicado y
                    exigente que resolvieron con total profesionalidad. El
                    resultado superó mis expectativas.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
